etball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After its exhibition against Team USA, Team Canada (Group A) begins the group phase against the winner of the Greece Olympic Qualifying Tournament on July 27.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2660, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3776165862000163e-25, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then Australia (July 30) and Spain (Aug. 2).\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2826, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2787, \"end\": 2796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9906703701554728, \"rank\": 0.009035739433772654, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2811, \"end\": 2816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999997783347926, \"rank\": 2.2038856914462646e-07, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ANDREW NEMBHARD, CANADA  Nembhard has the opportunity to join Olynyk with Team Canada after the 6-foot-5 guard accepted an invite to training camp following an impressive playoff debut with the Indiana Pacers.\", \"from\": 2828, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc